WEBVTT

00:00:27.780 --> 00:00:30.268
ingliz tili imlosida tovush unchalik ham

00:00:30.268 --> 00:00:32.414
ahamiyatga ega emas.

00:00:32.414 --> 00:00:35.695
So'zning ma'nosi va uning tarixi birinchi 
navbatda ahamiyatlidir.

00:00:35.695 --> 00:00:37.729
"To doubt" so'zi "shubhalanmoq",

00:00:37.729 --> 00:00:38.739
"ikkilanmoq",

00:00:38.739 --> 00:00:40.202
"tortinmoq" deganidir.

00:00:40.202 --> 00:00:43.780
Ot so'z turkumi sifatida u noaniqlik, 
adashish degan ma'nolarga ega.

00:00:43.780 --> 00:00:46.146
Zamonaviy ingliz tilidagi "doubt" so'zi

00:00:46.146 --> 00:00:49.786
lotincha "dubitare" so'zidan kelib 
chiqqan.

00:00:49.786 --> 00:00:52.211
U boshida lotinchadan fransuz tiliga 
o'tgan.

00:00:52.211 --> 00:00:56.471
Shunda u "b" tovushini va harfini 
yo'qotgan.

00:00:56.471 --> 00:00:59.421
Keyinchalik XIII asrda bu so'z ingliz 
tiliga kirib kelgan.

00:00:59.421 --> 00:01:01.347
Yuz yillarcha vaqt o'tib,